{"tid":520117,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"兩岸為台獨開戰　港媒：過半台人拒戰","createTime":"2018-01-05T05:30:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T05:54:58.000Z","uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aa33251cfd3469d23a512892a80ee0b2b19cfa16","tid":520117,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T05:30:00.000Z","msg":"2016大選過後，民進黨大獲全勝，進入全面執政的時期，也讓不少挺獨人士認為「台獨有望了」，然而中國大陸始終仍未放棄對台「武統」的想法。因此，一旦中國大陸真因台獨而發動戰爭，究竟有多少台灣人願意執干戈為台獨而戰？對此，港媒以2016總統大選投給蔡英文的投票比例56%來看，認為如果扣掉當中的反戰者，恐怕最後會連50%都還不到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港媒《中國評論通訊社》元旦時發表評論指出，台灣若想和美、日綑綁，屆時兩岸若發生戰爭，台灣就得直接面對中國大陸。儘管蔡英文不時表示「不可一日無戰備」，但就算蔡英文真準備好了，那台灣民眾呢？是否願意拿起武器為台獨而戰？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場加映chenglap<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n編輯: 「去調查有多少人願意為臺獨而戰. 看是否少過一半. 」<br />\n記者: 「如果少過一半呢? 」<br />\n編輯: 「說少過一半, 嘲笑臺灣人沒膽臺獨. 」<br />\n記者: 「如果剛好一半呢? 」<br />\n編輯: 「說臺灣人不團結, 社會撕裂. 」<br />\n記者: 「如果多過一半呢? 」<br />\n編輯: 「說超過一半人願意為不切實際的政治理想投入戰爭, 臺灣是個法西斯的軍國主義國家. 」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=332612\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D332612&d=RS8OccpzGdwe2pTUvewOpRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=77ea6ed8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D332612&h=aa11bccb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=332612</a>"},{"pid":"a3e91cae4ae41d6c837f10090e7a02c7a827f858","tid":520117,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T05:39:03.000Z","msg":"開錯台呀ching"},{"pid":"35f51628a9d34aaebce20871ed5e89f9815f6fb0","tid":520117,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T05:54:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}